<section id="readingText">
	<h1>Writing Task 1</h1>
	<p>You should spend about 20 minutes on this task.</p>
	<p><b>A series of radio programmes which you enjoyed finished recently. Write a letter to the radio station. Thank them for the series and tell them why you enjoyed it. Ask if they are going to broadcast similar programmes in the future.</b></p>
	<p>You should write at least 150 words.</p>
	<p>You do NOT need to write your own address.</p>
	<p>Begin your letter as follows:</p><p>Dear Sir/Madam,</p>
